<h2>Privacy Policy</h2>
<ul>
    <li><strong>Site owner:</strong> Silvia (<a href="https://sentimentalfuturist.net">sentimentalfuturist.net</a>)</li>
    <li><strong>Location:</strong> Spain</li>
</ul>
<p>This page explains what data is collected when you visit this site and why.</p>

<h3>What I collect</h3>
<ul>
    <li>
        <strong>Analytics:</strong> I use <a href="https://www.goatcounter.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">GoatCounter</a> to see if visitors use mobile or desktop and what browsers they use. It does not use cookies, and no personal data is stored.</li>
    <li>
        <strong>Guestbook:</strong> If you sign my <a href="/guestbook/">guestbook</a>, you choose to share your Name, Website URL, and Message. This data is stored by the service provider, <a href="https://guestbooks.meadow.cafe/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Meadow.cafe</a>, not by me directly.
        <ul>
            <li>
                You can check the Guestbook's terms and conditions here: <a href="https://guestbooks.meadow.cafe/terms-and-conditions" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Terms and Conditions</a>
            </li>
        </ul>
    </li>
    <li>
        <strong>Embedded content:</strong> Some posts may contain embedded videos or media from third-party sites, such as:
        <ul>
            <li>Videos from <a href="https://www.youtube.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">YouTube</a>: <a href="https://www.youtube.com/howyoutubeworks/our-commitments/protecting-user-data/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Privacy Policy</a>
            </li>
        </ul>
    </li>
</ul>

<h3>What I don't do</h3>
<ul>
    <li>I don't sell or share your data.</li>
    <li>I don't track you across other websites.</li>
    <li>I don't use cookies for advertising.</li>
</ul>

<h3>Your rights</h3>
<p>Under Spanish/EU law, you have the right to ask me to delete any data I hold about you or to ask how I use your information. You can <a href="/contact/">send me an e-mail</a>.</p>

